Class VelocitySensorData

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.data.SensorData
      • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.data.VelocitySensorData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IData

    public class VelocitySensorData
extends SensorData
    Contains one set of values of the RMCSs velocity-sensors. If the RMCS is equipped with a 3-axis accelerometer and/or gyroscope, this class could be edited to accommodate that sensor-data.
    Author:
    Boeck
